creator: Homecare Network
descriptionHtml:
Homecare platform is designed to assist Homecare industry to cope with the increasing number of client with complex care needs.

Our scheduling system connects the best available qualified caregivers to patients based on patient’s specific location, needs and preferences.

Homecare for Caregiver App provides an easy method to view upcoming scheduled cares, connect to clients and manage individual profile.
descriptionShort: Access to upcoming visits, jobs and documents including real-time alerts.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
Improvements
- Drop-pin on map to specify current location
- Show full-address on Trip, Client, My Profile, Contact details screen
- Show full Job name on Job details screen
- Show all Qualifications on My Profile screen

Fixes
- Incorrectly obtain current GPS location in some situations
